              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Compact velocity filter"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC",
                "PSSSD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Fusion evaporation residues were detected",
                "using a compact velocity filter and a hybrid  detector.",
                "The latter consisted of a position-sensitive,",
                "multiwire, gas proportional detector backed with a",
                "stopping position-sensitive silicon surface barrier",
                "detector.  The velocity filter transmitted the",
                "evaporation residues to the detector whilst deflecting",
                "the intense elastically scattered beam particles to one",
                "side, where they were intercepted by a movable tantalum",
                "finger.  With this arrangement, the evaporation",
                "residues could be precisely measured at angles as small",
                "as 1 degree with respect to the beam axis."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "3AULCBR"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The 14UD Pelletron accelerator"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The accelerator provided pulsed 32,34S beams (~1",
                "ns wide beam bursts separated by 530 ns)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  The evaporation residues were identified by the",
                "energy deposited in the silicon surface barrier",
                "detector and the time of flight relative to the pulsed",
                "beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
